controllers.publix.workers

Class MTPublix

  • java.lang.Object
    • play.mvc.Results
      • play.mvc.Controller
        • controllers.publix.Publix<MTWorker>
          • controllers.publix.workers.MTPublix
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IPublix, play.mvc.Http.HeaderNames, play.mvc.Http.Status

    @Singleton
public class MTPublix
extends Publix<MTWorker>
implements IPublix
    Implementation of JATOS' public API for studies that are started via MTurk. A MTurk run is done by a MTWorker or a MTSandboxWorker.
